<component type="desktop">
	<id>com.thomasokken.free42</id>
	<name>Free42</name>
	<summary>Free42 is a re-implementation of the HP-42S Scientific Programmable Calculator and HP-82240 Printer.</summary>
	<developer_name>Thomas Okken</developer_name>
	<launchable type="desktop-id">com.thomasokken.free42.desktop</launchable>
	<metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
	<project_license>GPL-2.0</project_license>
	<description>
		<p>Free42 is a complete rewrite, not using any HP code. It does not require an HP-42S ROM image. Even though it contains significant enhancements compared to the original calculator, Free42 remains fully compatible with the HP-42S, bothin its user interface and in its ability to run programs written for the HP-42S.</p>
	</description>
